title: Added test for convertCircuitJsonToPcbSvg and generateLightBurnSvg.
description: This pull request introduces tests for the functions convertCircuitJsonToPcbSvg and generateLightBurnSvg, enhancing the reliability and maintainability of the codebase by ensuring that these functions behave as expected under various conditions. The addition of a new dependency, stack-svgs, is also included to support the new functionality.

title: Prevent Full App Crashes from Unhandled React Render Errors by Introducing a Reusable ErrorBoundary with Localized Reset Recovery
description: Introduces a reusable ErrorBoundary component that catches unhandled render and lifecycle errors, prevents full-app crashes, displays a safe fallback UI, logs error information, and allows localized recovery via a reset action.
body:
This PR introduces a reusable ErrorBoundary component that:
- Catches unhandled render and lifecycle errors
- Prevents full-app crashes
- Displays a safe, user-facing fallback UI
- Logs detailed error information to the console
- Allows localized recovery via a "Reset section" action

title: Introduce Deterministic SVG Snapshot Testing with Bun Preload Integraion
description: Add SVG snapshot testing via bun-match-svg to ensure stable, regression-proof SVG output
body:
- Add SVG snapshot testing via bun-match-svg to ensure stable, regression-proof SVG output  
- Configure bunfig.toml test preload for zero-friction matcher setup  
- Include example test and baseline snapshot to establish the testing pattern
